### Architecture Knowledge Agent — REST API requests
### Works with the VS Code "REST Client" extension or the JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Start the API first: dotnet run --project src/AkAgent.Api

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5024

### Ask a question (Q&A)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json
# X-Api-Key: your-api-key-here

{
  "question": "How do services communicate?"
}

### Validate a planned approach (guardrail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/validate
Content-Type: application/json
# X-Api-Key: your-api-key-here

{
  "proposal": "add a new message queue"
}

### Trigger a manual sync
POST {{baseUrl}}/sync
# X-Api-Key: your-api-key-here

### Readiness / per-source sync status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status
# X-Api-Key: your-api-key-here

### List all indexed documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents
# X-Api-Key: your-api-key-here

### Get a single document by id
### Replace the id with one returned from the /documents request above.
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/FileDrop:adr-002.md
# X-Api-Key: your-api-key-here
